<li role="presentation"><a href='?term="Mutat%20Res"[jour]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem" data-add-to-search="true">Add to search</a></li>
</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Dietary folic acid protects against genotoxicity in the red blood cells of mice</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="MacFarlane%20AJ"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Amanda J MacFarlane</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Amanda J MacFarlane</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>a</sup>Nutrition Research Division, Health Canada, Ottawa, Canada</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="MacFarlane%20AJ"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Amanda J MacFarlane</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>a,</sup><sup>*</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Behan%20NA"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Nathalie A Behan</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3><span class="name western">Nathalie A Behan</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>a</sup>Nutrition Research Division, Health Canada, Ottawa, Canada</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Behan%20NA"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Nathalie A Behan</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>a</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Field%20MS"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Martha S Field</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3><span class="name western">Martha S Field</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>b</sup>Division of Nutritional Sciences, Cornell University, Ithaca, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Field%20MS"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Martha S Field</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>b</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Williams%20A"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Andrew Williams</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3><span class="name western">Andrew Williams</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>c</sup>Environmental Health Science and Research Bureau, Health Canada, Ottawa, Canada</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Williams%20A"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Andrew Williams</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>c</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Stover%20PJ"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id5"><span class="name western">Patrick J Stover</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id5">
<h3><span class="name western">Patrick J Stover</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>b</sup>Division of Nutritional Sciences, Cornell University, Ithaca, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Stover%20PJ"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Patrick J Stover</span></a>
